{"tid":2105913,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 12 pro因加入lidar，電池縮水？12系列電量最多僅有3687mAh","createTime":"2020-07-13T03:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T05:49:44.000Z","uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae5eb779142bd0bd6af7c91f0cf5cc5d67fdb84","tid":2105913,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"據數碼瘋報爆料，三款新iPhone電池通過認證，容量分別為2227mAh、2775mAh、3687mAh。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YT68JP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YT68JP.png&h=1355f339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從該微博爆料的內容來看，三款新iPhone電池分別為 A2471：2227mAh、A2431：2775mAh、A2466：3687mAh，均是額定電池容量。此外，A2466還採用L型電池，是三款電池中容量最大的一款。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，今年蘋果將推出四款iPhone 12機型，分別為包括一款5.4英吋（iPhone12）、兩款6.1英吋（iPhone12 Max、iPhone 12 Pro）以及一款6.7英吋機型（iPhone12 Pro Max）。<br />\n<br />\n如此看來，這三款新電池很有可能就是iPhone 12的電池<br />\n<br />\n5.4吋機型應該使用的是A2471：2227mAh<br />\n<br />\n兩款6.1吋機型使用的是A2431：2775mAh<br />\n<br />\n而6.7吋機型使用的則是A2466：3687mAh<br />\n<br />\n與之相比，iPhone 11電池容量為3110mAh，iPhone 11 Pro電池容量為3190mAh，iPhone 11 Pro Max電池容量為3500mAh。除了iPhone 12除了6.7英吋機型，其餘三款電池均小於iPhone 11系列機型，對於重度使用的用戶來說並不是一個好消息。"},{"pid":"6f666fc4544a299827603550a1c259802301833b","tid":2105913,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"更正：iPhone 11 Pro Max 電池容量為3,969 mAh <br />\n<br />\n抄都抄錯，啲編輯點寫嘢嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9a49ee95c940abdb9ff09ece88b80c8ba92ec5","tid":2105913,"uid":78492,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"加個Lidar有咩用？"},{"pid":"0ad4c7771e73006610704e00d543809f0e078728","tid":2105913,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9a49ee95c940abdb9ff09ece88b80c8ba92ec5","tid":2105913,"uid":78492,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"加個Lidar有咩用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"